{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2020/06/03-first-post/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Into the Blue Hour"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ae78fd3d-aaff-582b-ac7a-44c824ec141d","excerpt":"Hello! This is my very first blog post‚Ä¶ ‚Ä¶built on Jekyll. In November 2018, I taught myself how to build a website. When I was looking for a free platform to‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hello! This is my very first blog post‚Ä¶</p>\n<p>‚Ä¶built on Jekyll.</p>\n<p>In November 2018, I taught myself how to build a website. When I was looking for a free platform to publish it, I found this static site generator.</p>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.64864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Jekyll&#39;s quick start instructions.\"\n        title=\"Jekyll&#39;s quick start instructions.\"\n        src=\"/static/73bb01890a8e1d9e53fcc421c515491b/1c72d/jekyll-quick-start.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/73bb01890a8e1d9e53fcc421c515491b/a80bd/jekyll-quick-start.jpg 148w,\n/static/73bb01890a8e1d9e53fcc421c515491b/1c91a/jekyll-quick-start.jpg 295w,\n/static/73bb01890a8e1d9e53fcc421c515491b/1c72d/jekyll-quick-start.jpg 590w,\n/static/73bb01890a8e1d9e53fcc421c515491b/a8a14/jekyll-quick-start.jpg 885w,\n/static/73bb01890a8e1d9e53fcc421c515491b/ec5dd/jekyll-quick-start.jpg 941w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n  <figcaption>Jekyll's quick start instructions.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>How the hell do I run it? What is ‚Äúgem‚Äù?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Pretty much that was my first impression. Even though the site said ‚Äúsimple‚Äù, I didn‚Äôt think it was. A <strong>big no</strong> for me. Then I found <a href=\"https://pages.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Github Pages</a> and stayed with it.</p>\n<p>It was long until recently I wanted to write again (pst, I used to be a blogger on <a href=\"http://lpiblogsite.blogspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Linkin Park Indonesia</a>). I visited Jekyll yesterday and wow! Things got simpler after I graduated from a coding bootcamp. Now I know what those commands mean. Written in Ruby, <code class=\"language-text\">gem</code> is like <code class=\"language-text\">node</code>, and <code class=\"language-text\">Gemfile</code> is like <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> in Javascript.</p>\n<p>There are so many cool templates but I picked Noir and tweaked it a little bit. Minimalist, well-organized, and does not focus on the image.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>You are a web developer now. So why don‚Äôt you build your own?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It‚Äôs time-consuming at the moment. Besides, I want to focus on the content instead. There will be diverse topics, be it music, technology, or even some rants. I don‚Äôt set a fixed theme for this blog.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Why do you name it ‚ÄúInto the Blue Hour‚Äù?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It is my favorite moment of the day‚Äîa peaceful transition into tranquility.</p>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.972972972972975%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Blue hour\"\n        title=\"Blue hour\"\n        src=\"/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/1c72d/id.pinterest.com.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/a80bd/id.pinterest.com.jpg 148w,\n/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/1c91a/id.pinterest.com.jpg 295w,\n/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/1c72d/id.pinterest.com.jpg 590w,\n/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/a8a14/id.pinterest.com.jpg 885w,\n/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/fbd2c/id.pinterest.com.jpg 1180w,\n/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/01afc/id.pinterest.com.jpg 5503w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n  <figcaption>Blue hour (source: <a href=\"https://wirelesssoul.net/blue-hour-wallpaper-high-definition/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wireless Soul</a>)</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>See you on the next post! üëã</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"First Post","date":"June 3rd, 2020","last_modified_at":"June 6th, 2020","categories":["Other"],"description":"Jumping on a new platform","link":"(supposed to be a link but I'll leave this here for GraphQL's sake)","tags":["random"],"image":{"publicURL":"/static/c8b9391dd539f84428c80b353972b778/id.pinterest.com.jpg"}},"timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2020/06/03-first-post/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2020/06/05-migrating-to-gatsbyjs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Migrating to GatsbyJS"}}}}}